title: Sibling Watchery - Drag Race UK Season 3 - Episode 8
description:
This week Monét X Change is joined by Laila McQueen to discuss the latest episode of the never ending season of Drag Race UK. The two dive into this week's challenges and don't hold back their opinions on who they think deserves to go home already! Tune in to hear all the drama!!
